Class JSONArray

java.lang.Object
json.JSONValue
json.JSONArray
All Implemented Interfaces:
Iterable<JSONValue>
public class JSONArray extends JSONValue implements Iterable<JSONValue>
Represents a mutable JSON Array. Each JSON Array contains an ordered list of values.
